Package myAdapter

Contiene le classi e interfacce che implementano l'adapter

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HCollection
    The root interface in the collection hierarchy.
    HIterator
    An iterator over a collection.
    HList
    An ordered collection (also known as a sequence).
    HListIterator
    An iterator for lists that allows the programmer to traverse the list in either direction, modify the list during iteration, and obtain the iterator's current position in the list.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ListAdapter
    ListAdapter e' una classe che implementa tutti i metodi delle classi Collection e List di Java 2 Runtime Environment, J2RE 1.4.2.
    SubList
    SubList e' una classe che permette di operare in un intervallo di una lista tra i valori from, incluso, e to, escluso.
    Vector
    Class Vector of Java Micro Edition, CLDC1.1
    The object Vector is used to save e manage data, the purpose of this class is only to filter the methods of vector in order to use only methods from CLDC1.1
